## AI Patterns Used
- **Agentic AI Patterns**: Self-Correction / Critic pattern for verification.
- **Strategy Pattern**: Pluggable validators within the governance framework.
- **Chain of Responsibility**: Sequential processing of safety and validity checks.
- **SOLID/DRY**: Shared base classes and interfaces for all governance components.
